<h2><%= @study.name %></h2>

<p>This study is <b>not</b> conducted by or supervised by the Personal
Genome Project.  You can read about the study here, then decide
whether to carry on to the study&rsquo;s own independent web site.</p>

<p><%=raw CGI.escapeHTML(@study.participant_description).gsub("\r","").gsub("\n\n","</p><p>").gsub("\n","<br />") %></p>

<p><b>Researcher</b>: <%= @study.researcher.full_name %>, <%= @study.researcher.researcher_affiliation %></p>

<div style="width:300px;padding:1em;border:1px dashed #866">
  Clicking the "participate" button below will take you to the third-party study&rsquo;s web site.  A token will be passed to confirm that you are a PGP participant &mdash; but this will not identify <i>which</i> PGP participant you are.
  <br />&nbsp;
  <div style="text-align:center">
    <%= button_to 'Participate in this study', clickthrough_to_third_party_study_path(@study) %>
  </div>
</div>
